address2: Eco and Techno Development Zone Ganzhe Street Minhou County
longBusinessSummary: Yamada Green Resources Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the production and sale of fresh and processed food products in Japan and the People's Republic of China. The company operates through Processed Food Products, Investment Properties, and Corporate segments. Its processed food products include water-boiled/dried vegetables, such as bamboo shoots, carrots, radishes, burdocks, chestnuts, and dried shiitake mushrooms; and konjac-based dietary fiber food products comprising instant noodles and desserts. The company distributes processed and semi-processed food products primarily through local supermarket chains, distributor, and convenience stores. In addition, it is involved in office and logistics property rental activities, and sale of edible fungi. Yamada Green Resources Limited was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Fuzhou, China.
